				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">4. Inquiries & Communications</h2>
					<p>Information submitted through our contact form is used solely for responding to your inquiry. Submission of an inquiry does not create a contractual obligation on either party. Formal agreements are subject to separate written contracts.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
					<p>PT. Indo Energy Tekniko shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this website. We make no warranties regarding the accuracy or completeness of information presented on this site.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">6. External Links</h2>
					<p>This website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of external sites.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">7. Governing Law</h2>
					<p>These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Republic of Indonesia. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Jakarta, Indonesia.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
					<p>We reserve the right to update these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this website.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">9. Contact</h2>
					<p>For questions regarding these terms, please contact us at:</p>
					<p class="mt-2 font-medium text-navy-900">sales@indoenergytekniko.com</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
